1993", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC1435.html", target="_top", tooltip="In the course of reviewing the MTU Discovery protocol for possible elevation to Draft Standard, a specific operational problem was uncovered.  The problem results from the optional suppression of ICMP messages implemented in some routers.  This memo outlines a modification to this practice to allow the correct functioning of MTU Discovery.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard."];
